snippet.title: ☆ Mavericks: Proving Grounds - HD Teaser Trailer ☆
snippet.description:
Mavericks: Proving Grounds - Official Reveal Trailer (New Battle Royale Multiplayer game possibly releasing late 2018). The game will feature a 400 player battle royale experience. 
The game's website: http://mavericks.gg/
Note this is a teaser trailer, please stop commenting about the lack of content this trailer provides. We all know.
